<h2>2 - Town Creek Church Bridge (a/k/a Garnett Bridge) to Copper Mine (Grindle Falls/Grindle Shoals Section)</h2>
<table class='data_table river-stats'>
<tr class='row-1'>
<th>Usual Difficulty</th>
<td>II-V (for normal flows) </td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-2'>
<th>Length</th>
<td>3.8 Miles </td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-3'>
<th>Avg. Gradient</th>
<td>50 fpm</td>
</tr>
</table>
